name: Turtwig
flavorText: Made from soil, the shell on itsback hardens when it drinks water.It lives along lakes.

name: Grotle
flavorText: It knows where pure water wellsup. It carries fellow Pokémon thereon its back.

name: Torterra
flavorText: Small Pokémon occasionally gatheron its unmoving back to beginbuilding their nests.

name: Chimchar
flavorText: It agilely scales sheer cliffs tolive atop craggy mountains. Itsfire is put out when it sleeps.

name: Monferno
flavorText: To intimidate attackers, itstretches the fire on its tailto make itself appear bigger.

name: Infernape
flavorText: It uses a special kind of martialarts involving all its limbs.Its fire never goes out.

name: Piplup
flavorText: Because it is very proud, it hatesaccepting food from people. Itsthick down guards it from cold.

name: Prinplup
flavorText: It lives alone, away from others.Apparently, every one of thembelieves it is the most important.

name: Empoleon
flavorText: The three horns that extend fromits beak attest to its power. Theleader has the biggest horns.

name: Starly
flavorText: They flock in great numbers.Though small, they flap theirwings with great power.

name: Staravia
flavorText: It flies around forests and fieldsin search of bug Pokémon.It stays within a huge flock.

name: Staraptor
flavorText: It has a savage nature. It willcourageously challenge foes thatare much larger.

name: Bidoof
flavorText: With nerves of steel, nothing canperturb it. It is more agile andactive than it appears.

name: Bibarel
flavorText: It makes its nest by dammingstreams with bark and mud. It isknown as an industrious worker.

name: Kricketot
flavorText: It shakes its head back to front,causing its antennae to hit eachother and sound like a xylophone.

name: Kricketune
flavorText: It crosses its knifelike arms infront of its chest when it cries.It can compose melodies ad lib.

name: Shinx
flavorText: All of its fur dazzles if danger issensed. It flees while the foe ismomentarily blinded.

name: Luxio
flavorText: Its claws loose electricity withenough amperage to cause fainting.They live in small groups.

name: Luxray
flavorText: It has eyes that can see throughanything. It spots and capturesprey hiding behind objects.

name: Budew
flavorText: Over the winter, it closes its budand endures the cold. In spring,the bud opens and releases pollen.

name: Roserade
flavorText: It attracts prey with a sweetaroma, then downs it withthorny whips hidden in its arms.

name: Cranidos
flavorText: It lived in jungles around 100million years ago. Its skull is ashard as iron.

name: Rampardos
flavorText: Its powerful head butt has enoughpower to shatter even the mostdurable things upon impact.

name: Shieldon
flavorText: A Pokémon that lived in junglesaround 100 million years ago. Itsfacial hide is extremely hard.

name: Bastiodon
flavorText: Any frontal attack is repulsed.It is a docile Pokémon thatfeeds on grass and berries.

name: Burmy
flavorText: To shelter itself from cold, wintrywinds, it covers itself with a cloakmade of twigs and leaves.

name: Wormadam-plant
flavorText: When BURMY evolved, its cloakbecame a part of this Pokémon’sbody. The cloak is never shed.

name: Mothim
flavorText: It loves the honey of flowersand steals honey collected byCOMBEE.

name: Combee
flavorText: A Pokémon formed by three others.It busily carries sweet floralhoney to VESPIQUEN.

name: Vespiquen
flavorText: Its abdomen is a honeycomb forgrubs. It raises its grubs onhoney collected by COMBEE.

name: Pachirisu
flavorText: It makes fur balls that cracklewith static electricity. It storesthem with berries in tree holes.

name: Buizel
flavorText: It has a flotation sac that islike an inflatable collar. It floatson water with its head out.

name: Floatzel
flavorText: It floats using its well-developedflotation sac. It assists in therescues of drowning people.

name: Cherubi
flavorText: The small ball holds the nutrientsneeded for evolution. Apparently,it is very sweet and tasty.

name: Cherrim
flavorText: It blooms during times of strongsunlight. It tries to make up foreverything it endured as a bud.

name: Shellos
flavorText: Its colors and shapes differ fromregion to region. In the Sinnohregion, two types are confirmed.

name: Gastrodon
flavorText: It has a pliable body without anybones. If any part of its body istorn off, it grows right back.

name: Ambipom
flavorText: To eat, it deftly shucks nutswith its two tails. It rarely usesits arms now.

name: Drifloon
flavorText: A Pokémon formed by the spiritsof people and Pokémon. It lovesdamp, humid seasons.

name: Drifblim
flavorText: At dusk, swarms of them arecarried aloft on winds. Whennoticed, they suddenly vanish.

name: Buneary
flavorText: It slams foes by sharply uncoilingits rolled ears. It stings enoughto make a grown-up cry in pain.

name: Lopunny
flavorText: An extremely cautious Pokémon.It cloaks its body with its fluffyear fur when it senses danger.

name: Mismagius
flavorText: Its cries sound like incantations.Those hearing it are tormentedby headaches and hallucinations.

name: Honchkrow
flavorText: Becoming active at night, it isknown to swarm with numerousMURKROW in tow.

name: Glameow
flavorText: It claws if displeased and purrswhen affectionate. Its ficklenessis very popular among some.

name: Purugly
flavorText: It is a brazen brute that bargesits way into another Pokémon’snest and claims it as its own.

name: Chingling
flavorText: It emits cries by agitating an orbat the back of its throat.It moves with flouncing hops.

name: Stunky
flavorText: It protects itself by spraying anoxious fluid from its rear. Thestench lingers for 24 hours.

name: Skuntank
flavorText: It sprays a vile-smelling fluidfrom the tip of its tail to attack.Its range is over 160 feet.

name: Bronzor
flavorText: Implements shaped like it werediscovered in ancient tombs. It isunknown if they are related.

name: Bronzong
flavorText: One caused a news sensation whenit was dug up at a constructionsite after a 2,000-year sleep.

name: Bonsly
flavorText: It looks as if it is always crying.It is actually adjusting its body’sfluid levels by eliminating excess.

name: Mime-jr
flavorText: It habitually mimics foes. Oncemimicked, the foe cannot take itseyes off this Pokémon.

name: Happiny
flavorText: It loves round white things.It carries an egg-shaped rock inimitation of CHANSEY.

name: Chatot
flavorText: It can learn and speak humanwords. If they gather, they alllearn the same saying.

name: Spiritomb
flavorText: A Pokémon that was formed by 108spirits. It is bound to a fissurein an odd keystone.

name: Gible
flavorText: It nests in small, horizontal holesin cave walls. It pounces to catchprey that stray too close.

name: Gabite
flavorText: There is a long-held belief thatmedicine made from its scales willheal even incurable illnesses.

name: Garchomp
flavorText: When it folds up its body andextends its wings, it looks like ajet plane. It flies at sonic speed.

name: Munchlax
flavorText: It wolfs down its weight in foodonce a day, swallowing food wholewith almost no chewing.

name: Riolu
flavorText: The aura that emanates from itsbody intensifies to alert othersif it is afraid or sad.

name: Lucario
flavorText: It has the ability to sense theauras of all things.It understands human speech.

name: Hippopotas
flavorText: It lives in arid places. Insteadof perspiration, it expels grainysand from its body.

name: Hippowdon
flavorText: It blasts internally stored sandfrom ports on its body to createa towering twister for attack.

name: Skorupi
flavorText: It grips prey with its tail clawsand injects poison. It tenaciouslyhangs on until the poison takes.

name: Drapion
flavorText: It has the power in its clawedarms to make scrap of a car. Thetips of its claws release poison.

name: Croagunk
flavorText: Its cheeks hold poison sacs.It tries to catch foes off guardto jab them with toxic fingers.

name: Toxicroak
flavorText: Its knuckle claws secrete a toxinso vile that even a scratch couldprove fatal.

name: Carnivine
flavorText: It attracts prey with its sweet-smelling saliva, then chomps down.It takes a whole day to eat prey.

name: Finneon
flavorText: After long exposure to sunlight,the patterns on its tail fins shinevividly when darkness arrives.

name: Lumineon
flavorText: It lives on the deep-sea floor.It attracts prey by flashing thepatterns on its four tail fins.

name: Mantyke
flavorText: A friendly Pokémon that capturesthe subtle flows of seawater usingits two antennae.

name: Snover
flavorText: It lives on snowy mountains.Having had little contact withhumans, it is boldly inquisitive.

name: Abomasnow
flavorText: It whips up blizzards in mountainsthat are always buried in snow.It is the abominable snowman.

name: Weavile
flavorText: They live in cold regions, forminggroups of four or five that huntprey with impressive coordination.

name: Magnezone
flavorText: It evolved from exposure to aspecial magnetic field.Three units generate magnetism.

name: Lickilicky
flavorText: It wraps things with its extensibletongue. Getting too close to itwill leave you soaked with drool.

name: Rhyperior
flavorText: It puts rocks in holes in its palmsand uses its muscles to shoot them.GEODUDE are shot at rare times.

name: Tangrowth
flavorText: It ensnares prey by extendingarms made of vines. Losing arms topredators does not trouble it.

name: Electivire
flavorText: As its electric charge amplifies,blue sparks begin to crackle betweenits horns.

name: Magmortar
flavorText: It blasts fireballs of over 3,600degrees F from the ends of itsarms. It lives in volcanic craters.

name: Togekiss
flavorText: It will never appear where thereis strife. Its sightings havebecome rare recently.

name: Yanmega
flavorText: By churning its wings, it createsshock waves that inflict criticalinternal injuries to foes.

name: Leafeon
flavorText: Just like a plant, it usesphotosynthesis. As a result, it isalways enveloped in clear air.

name: Glaceon
flavorText: As a protective technique, it cancompletely freeze its fur to makeits hairs stand like needles.

name: Gliscor
flavorText: It observes prey while hanginginverted from branches. When thechance presents itself, it swoops!

name: Mamoswine
flavorText: Its impressive tusks are made ofice. The population thinned when itturned warm after the ice age.

name: Porygon-z
flavorText: Additional software was installedto make it a better Pokémon.It began acting oddly, however.

name: Gallade
flavorText: A master of courtesy andswordsmanship, it fights usingextending swords on its elbows.

name: Probopass
flavorText: It freely controls three smallunits called Mini-Noses usingmagnetic force.

name: Dusknoir
flavorText: The antenna on its head capturesradio waves from the world of spiritsthat command it to take people there.

name: Froslass
flavorText: It freezes foes with an icy breathnearly -60 degrees F. What seemsto be its body is actually hollow.

name: Rotom
flavorText: Its body is composed of plasma. Itis known to infiltrate electronicdevices and wreak havoc.

name: Uxie
flavorText: Known as “The Being of Knowledge.”It is said that it can wipe out thememory of those who see its eyes.

name: Mesprit
flavorText: Known as “The Being of Emotion.”It taught humans the nobility ofsorrow, pain, and joy.

name: Azelf
flavorText: Known as “The Being of Willpower.”It sleeps at the bottom of a laketo keep the world in balance.

name: Dialga
flavorText: It has the power to control time.It appears in Sinnoh-region mythsas an ancient deity.

name: Palkia
flavorText: It has the ability to distortspace. It is described as a deityin Sinnoh-region mythology.

name: Heatran
flavorText: It dwells in volcanic caves. Itdigs in with its cross-shaped feetto crawl on ceilings and walls.

name: Regigigas
flavorText: There is an enduring legend thatstates this Pokémon towedcontinents with ropes.

name: Giratina-altered
flavorText: A Pokémon that is said to live in aworld on the reverse side of ours.It appears in an ancient cemetery.

name: Cresselia
flavorText: Shiny particles are released fromits wings like a veil. It is saidto represent the crescent moon.

name: Phione
flavorText: It drifts in warm seas. It always returns to where itwas born, no matter how far it may have drifted.

name: Manaphy
flavorText: Born on a cold seafloor, itwill swim great distances toreturn to its birthplace.

name: Darkrai
flavorText: It can lull people to sleep andmake them dream. It is activeduring nights of the new moon.

name: Shaymin-land
flavorText: It lives in flower patches andavoids detection by curling upto look like a flowering plant.

name: Arceus
flavorText: It is described in mythology asthe Pokémon that shaped theuniverse with its 1,000 arms.
